      "source_name": "estimate_revision_momentum",
      "description": "group_rank(ts_zscore(<revision_field>, <days>), <group>). Analyst estimate revision momentum (Jegadeesh & Livnat 2006). Fields like earnings revision, target price changes, and net recommendation shifts. Coverage ~55% - nanHandling=ON strongly recommended for this dataset.",
